v1.1.2 - events!

New Content:
+ Every 30 minutes, an event will trigger, giving every player a free boost. 
+ LIMITED EVENT: Alien Invasion! A random event that drops up to 4 different unique items! Collect them around the map!

Changes:
+ Enchant skip price now adjusts based on time remaining. (1m, 5m, 15m, 30m, 45m, 1h, 2h, 3h, 6h, 12h, 18h, 24h, 30h, 36h, 42h, 48h) [X]
+ Added a description to the Ore Glazer, indicating that it removes the 'Neon' effect. [X]
+ Brand new Centering Conveyor model, design idea by @tnt0gamer [X]
+ Enchanting is now 1.5x faster, if you're ingame. [X]

Bug Fixes:
+ Added an arrow to the Mastery in the onboarding. [X]
+ Alien Invasion (item) now has serials and appears in #crazy-unboxes . oops [X]
+ Mobile drag button no longer moves to the center of the plot after each placement.
+ Fixed an issue where selecting/removing the conveyor too quickly would break the tutorial. [X]
+ Fixed an issue where removing selected conveyor step would completely break tutorial if you deselected. [X]
+ Overcharged ore no longer explodes after it's been processed. [X]
+ P2W, Achievement, and Rebirth items have been removed from the index, unless you own them. [X]
+ Computer with clocks set incorrectly can now see correct enchanting times (no longer using UTC time on the client). [X]
+ Explosions no longer damage players, and now have a brand new look. [X]
+ Fixed a rare bug that caused loading to hang. This also fixes auto-rejoin occasionally breaking. [X]
+ Removed 1 precision decimals from item descriptions, and now all items use 2 decimal precision. [X]
+ Fixed a small issue with the base (mis-aligned parts) [X]
+ Ancient Scanner now acts like a real scanner, and the hitbox is fixed. [X]
+ Rebirth and Achievement items are now flagged as 'special' items, which means owning a Shiny Mythic will fill all index rewards below it (base, shiny, mythic). [X]
+ Fixed cloned ore getting stuck in teleporter senders or sometimes not being upgraded. [X]

Other:
+ Added a new event on the game page for the next update. [X]
+ Winners of Thumbnail contest have been awarded their prize. [X]
+ Added new thumbnails for the game. [X]
+ Reduced plot memory by a very large margin. Found a remnant of server-sided item rendering still existing, which has now been removed. [X]
